answers.body_markdown:
I found the problem. The new serializer from namesapce *System.Text.Json.Serialization* will not serialize fields that are lists. Newtonsoft serializer does. I forgot the setter and getter.
Wrong:

    public class X {
       ...
       IList&lt;Y&gt; SomeListProperty = new List&lt;Y&gt;();
    }

Right:

     public class X {
           ...
           IList&lt;Y&gt; SomeListProperty {get;set;} = new List&lt;Y&gt;();
        }

